
Galactic Crisis
===============

Galactic Crisis is a game of brinkmanship, set in a universe where two
powerful alien races hold enough firepower to render the galaxy lifeless
several times over.  It is inspired by Cris Crawford's Balance of Power.

Requirements
------------

The following libraries should be installed on your system (these are the
Debian names for the packages):

    liballegro4.2-dev or liballegro4.4-dev
    libfreetype6-dev (other Freetype2 versions may work also)
    libcgal-dev (tested with libcgal8)
